    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Application SW shall, at least once per driving cycle, test the SMU core alive monitor and its connection to the SMU standby by triggering the alive alarm using SMU_AliveTest() command as described in the user manual"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "StartupPhase3 in Start up code performs the Alive Alarm Test of SMU module"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below command is used to test this ESM"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "No Configuration required for this ESM from project side"
    },
